      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac86",
      "text": "        22. dbc",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac87",
      "text": "        23. dca",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac88",
      "text": "        24. dcb",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac89",
      "text": "        24通りだな！([ブルートフォース])",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac8a",
      "text": "        この24通りのうち組み合わせが同じものがある",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac8b",
      "text": "         table:組み合わせ\t",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac8c",
      "text": "          1\tabc\tacb\tbac\tbca\tcab\tcba",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac8d",
      "text": "          2\tabd\tadb\tbad\tbda\tdab\tdba",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac8e",
      "text": "          3\tacd\tadc\tcad\tcda\tdac\tdca",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac8f",
      "text": "          4\tbcd\tbdc\tcbd\tcdb\tdbc\tdcb",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac90",
      "text": "        したがって「abcdの4つの文字から3つの文字を抜き出す組み合わせ」は4通りだといえる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac91",
      "text": "         >5枚から3枚を選ぶ組み合わせの総数は、次のように考えるとよいでしょう。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac92",
      "text": "         > ・まず、順列と同様に「順序を考えて」数える。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac93",
      "text": "         > ・重複して数えてしまった分(重複度)で割り算する。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac94",
      "text": "          プログラマの数学p.134",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac95",
      "text": "        今回の場合は",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac96",
      "text": "         1. 「順列と同様に「順序を考えて」数える」と、24通り",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac97",
      "text": "          [$ _{4}\\mathrm{P}_{3}=4\\times3\\times2=24]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac98",
      "text": "         2. 「重複して数えてしまった分(重複度)で割り算する」",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac99",
      "text": "          重複した分は3つの文字の置換の総数",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac9a",
      "text": "           3つの文字の並べ方は[$ _{3}\\mathrm{P}_{3}=3\\times2\\times1=6]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac9b",
      "text": "          したがって",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac9c",
      "text": "          [$ \\frac{_{4}\\mathrm{P}_{3}}{_{3}\\mathrm{P}_{3}}=\\frac{24}{6}=4]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac9d",
      "text": "        したがって組み合わせの計算は",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac9e",
      "text": "        [$ _{n}\\mathrm{C}_{m}=\\frac{_{n}\\mathrm{P}_{m}}{_{m}\\mathrm{P}_{m}}]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5ac9f",
      "text": "　　さーて戻ってきた。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5aca0",
      "text": "　　では、集合の部分集合の数をどう表すかの問題だ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5aca1",
      "text": "　  パターンは[二項係数]に似てるんだよな",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5aca2",
      "text": "　  　1,1",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5aca3",
      "text": "　  　1,2,1",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5aca4",
      "text": "　  　1,3,3,1",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5aca5",
      "text": "　  　この数をうまく足す方法があれば良い",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5aca6",
      "text": "　  　　nとn+1を…こう…上手く使って…[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670338414
    },
    {
      "id": "638f59ede5172d00007ee185",
      "text": "　  　[強い初心者][yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1670339054,
      "updated": 1670339089
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5aca7",
      "text": "　  n個の要素から、0〜n個選ぶ組み合わせの総数はどうなるか？",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670383312
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5aca8",
      "text": "　   0個選ぶってなんだ…？[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670338416
    },
    {
      "id": "639005ca5e90c0000087c2c4",
      "text": "　   1. n個から0個選ぶ場合",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670383049,
      "updated": 1670383205
    },
    {
      "id": "639007595e90c0000087c2ce",
      "text": "　    [$ _n\\mathrm{C}_{0}]？",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670383447,
      "updated": 1670383450
    },
    {
      "id": "6390075c5e90c0000087c2cf",
      "text": "　    　こんなことできるんか？",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670383450,
      "updated": 1670383470
    },
    {
      "id": "639007705e90c0000087c2d0",
      "text": "　    　[$ _{n}\\mathrm{P}_{m}=n\\times(n-1)\\times\\cdots\\times(n-m+1)]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670383471,
      "updated": 1670383549
    },
    {
      "id": "639007eb5e90c0000087c2d1",
      "text": "　    　なのでm=0なら",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670383594,
      "updated": 1670383621
    },
    {
      "id": "639007f35e90c0000087c2d2",
      "text": "　    　[$ \\sout{_{n}\\mathrm{P}_{0}=n\\times(n-0+1)=n(n+1)}]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670383601,
      "updated": 1670405872
    },
    {
      "id": "639049d6e6003500005f395c",
      "text": "　    　　ここに誤りがあります。色々と方法はありますが、次のように考えてみましょう[hatori.icon]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670400471,
      "updated": 1670400472
    },
    {
      "id": "639049d8e6003500005f395d",
      "text": "       [$ {}_{n}\\mathrm{P}_{m}=n\\times(n-1)\\times\\cdots\\times(n-m+1)=\\frac{n!}{(n-m)!}]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670400472,
      "updated": 1670400472
    },
    {
      "id": "639049d8e6003500005f395e",
      "text": "       　（コメント：[階乗]は分かります？）",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670400472,
      "updated": 1670400472
    },
    {
      "id": "639049d8e6003500005f395f",
      "text": "       　したがって[$ {}_{n}\\mathrm{P}_{0}=\\frac{n!}{n!}=1]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670400472,
      "updated": 1670400472
    },
    {
      "id": "639049d8e6003500005f3960",
      "text": "        ついでながら書いておくと、[$ 0!=1]に注意して[$ {}_{n}\\mathrm{C}_{m}=\\frac{{}_{n}\\mathrm{P}_{m}}{{}_{m}\\mathrm{P}_{m}}=\\frac{n!}{m!(n-m)!}]となります",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670400472,
      "updated": 1670400472
    },
    {
      "id": "6390504a5e90c000005e979c",
      "text": "        あざます！[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670402120,
      "updated": 1670402130
    },
    {
      "id": "639050545e90c000005e979d",
      "text": "        　帰ったらなぜズレたのか考えます！",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670402131,
      "updated": 1670402173
    },
    {
      "id": "6390507e5e90c000005e979e",
      "text": "        　階乗は1*2*3を3!で表すという[乃木わかる]程度にわかる",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1670402173,
      "updated": 1670403321
    },
    {
      "id": "63905e285e90c000009f78cf",
      "text": "        　　誰？",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670405671,
      "updated": 1670405675
    },
    {
      "id": "639008915e90c0000087c2d4",
      "text": "　    　[$ _{m}\\mathrm{P}_{m}=m\\times(m-m+1)=m]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670383760,
      "updated": 1670383897
    },
    {
      "id": "639009335e90c0000087c2d5",
      "text": "　    　なのでm=0なら0通り…？",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670383922,
      "updated": 1670384507
    },
    {
      "id": "639009505e90c0000087c2d7",
      "text": "　    　　[ゼロ除算]というのになりそう。このルートはダメだ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670383950,
      "updated": 1670384086
    },
    {
      "id": "63900b7f5e90c000000f14c4",
      "text": "        [$ _{n}\\mathrm{C}_{0}=\\frac{_{n}\\mathrm{P}_{0}}{_{0}\\mathrm{P}_{0}}=\\frac{n(n+1)}{0}=?]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670384510,
      "updated": 1670384649
    },
    {
      "id": "63900e915e90c000000f14c7",
      "text": "       計算をミスしてはいないか？",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670385295,
      "updated": 1670385330
    },
    {
      "id": "639006675e90c0000087c2ca",
      "text": "　   　何も選ばない場合(「ば」、「い」がややこしい)",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670383205,
      "updated": 1670383244
    },
    {
      "id": "639005e45e90c0000087c2c6",
      "text": "　    要素は1つもないので空集合になる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670383075,
      "updated": 1670383092
    },
    {
      "id": "639005f65e90c0000087c2c7",
      "text": "　   2. n個から1個えらぶ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670383093,
      "updated": 1670383129
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5aca9",
      "text": "　   sum関数みたいなことをやりたいのだがうーむ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5acaa",
      "text": "     これはあれだ、[$ \\Sigma]だ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337346
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55415e90c00000b3794b",
      "text": "     [総和]←赤リンク",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337858,
      "updated": 1670337870
    },
    {
      "id": "638f566d5e90c00000b3794d",
      "text": "    総和ってどうやったっけな……",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670338158,
      "updated": 1670338173
    },
    {
      "id": "638f567d5e90c00000b3794f",
      "text": "    [ライブ講義 大学1年生のための数学入門]p.36",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670338173,
      "updated": 1670338208
    },
    {
      "id": "638f56a65e90c00000b37950",
      "text": "     数列の和を表すのには[$ \\sum]を使う",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670338215,
      "updated": 1670338263
    },
    {
      "id": "638f56d75e90c00000b37951",
      "text": "     >数列[$ (a_1, a_2, a_3,\\cdots)]について，第[$ p]項から第[$ q]項までの和[$ a_p+a_{p+1}\\cdots+a_q]のことを(ただし[$ p, q]は整数で，[$ p\\leq q]とする)，",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670338263,
      "updated": 1670338719
    },
    {
      "id": "638f57a55e90c00000b3795d",
      "text": "     > [$ \\sum_{n=p}^qa_n]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670338470,
      "updated": 1670338687
    },
    {
      "id": "638f58835e90c00000b3795e",
      "text": "     >と書く。(定義)",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670338692,
      "updated": 1670338699
    },
    {
      "id": "63900cc75e90c000000f14c5",
      "text": "     総和ルートだと数列に落とし込まないといけない",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670384838,
      "updated": 1670384865
    },
    {
      "id": "63900ce25e90c000000f14c6",
      "text": "     　n-1個とn個だとどう表現するのか",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670384865,
      "updated": 1670384897
    },
    {
      "id": "638f53415e90c00000a5acab",
      "text": "   >いまここ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337346,
      "updated": 1670337969
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55ad5e90c00000b3794c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670337965,
      "updated": 1670337965
    },
    {
      "id": "63906602e600350000a1ca4d",
      "text": "恐らく\"サブクエスト\"に時間がかかりすぎるのは不本意だと思うので、なるべく[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]さんのやろうとしている方法に従いつつ解答(の一歩手前)を考えてみました[hatori.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670407683,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca4f",
      "text": " （[* 注意]：これが唯一の証明方法あるいは最も簡単な証明方法というわけではありません。たぶん）",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca50",
      "text": "　用語の定義１：与えられた集合[$ A]の部分集合全体を[$ \\mathfrak{P}(A)]と表し、[$ A]の[冪集合]と呼ぶ",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca51",
      "text": "　 [$ \\mathfrak{P}(A)]は集合の集合です",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca52",
      "text": "　　[$ \\mathfrak{P}]はPower setの頭文字Pの[フラクトゥール]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca53",
      "text": "　　[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/冪集合 冪集合 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca54",
      "text": "　用語の定義２：有限集合[$ A]の要素の個数を[$ |A|]と表す（無限集合の場合は要素の個数ではなく[濃度]という）",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca55",
      "text": "　　[$ \\#A]や[$ \\mathrm{card}(A)]とも表す",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca56",
      "text": "　　[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/濃度_(数学) 濃度 (数学) - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca57",
      "text": "　用語の定義３：集合[$ A]と[$ B]が共通部分を持たないとき、和集合[$ A\\cup B]を[$ A]と[$ B]の(集合論的)[直和]あるいは[非交和]とよぶ（このとき特に記号を変えて[$ A\\sqcup B]とも書く）",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca58",
      "text": "　　[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/和集合 和集合 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca59",
      "text": "いま[$ X_{3}=\\{1,2,3\\}]とおき、[$ |\\mathfrak{P}(X_{3})|=2^{3}]となることを示します",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca5a",
      "text": "　[/villagepump/問：n個の要素からなる集合の部分集合は全部で2^n個あることを示せ#638f53415e90c00000a5ac3c]の例に従って集合[$ A \\in \\mathfrak{P}(X_{3})]を要素の個数で分類します（いま[$ |X_{3}|=3]より、[$ 0 \\le |A| \\le 3]であることに注意）",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca5b",
      "text": "　 [$ |A|=0]の場合：[$ A = \\emptyset]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca5c",
      "text": "　 　3つの相異なるものから何も選ばない方法は[$ {}_{3}\\mathrm{C}_{0}]通り",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca5d",
      "text": "　 　よって[$ |\\{A\\in\\mathfrak{P}(X_{3}) ; |A|=0\\}|={}_{3}\\mathrm{C}_{0}]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca5e",
      "text": "　 [$ |A|=1]の場合：[$ A \\in \\{\\{1\\},\\{2\\},\\{3\\}\\}]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca5f",
      "text": "　 　3つの相異なるものから1つのものを選ぶ方法は[$ {}_{3}\\mathrm{C}_{1}]通り",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca60",
      "text": "　 　よって[$ |\\{A\\in\\mathfrak{P}(X_{3}) ; |A|=1\\}|={}_{3}\\mathrm{C}_{1}]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca61",
      "text": "　 [$ |A|=2]の場合：[$ A \\in \\{\\{1,2\\},\\{2,3\\},\\{1,3\\}\\}]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca62",
      "text": "　　　3つの相異なるものから2つのものを選ぶ方法は[$ {}_{3}\\mathrm{C}_{2}]通り",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca63",
      "text": "　　　よって[$ |\\{A\\in\\mathfrak{P}(X_{3}) ; |A|=2\\}|={}_{3}\\mathrm{C}_{2}]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca64",
      "text": "　 [$ |A|=3]の場合：[$ A =\\{1,2,3\\}]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca65",
      "text": "　 　3つの相異なるものから3つのものを選ぶ方法は[$ {}_{3}\\mathrm{C}_{3}]通り",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca66",
      "text": "　 　よって[$ |\\{A\\in\\mathfrak{P}(X_{3}) ; |A|=3\\}|={}_{3}\\mathrm{C}_{3}]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca67",
      "text": " したがって（一般の[$ n]に対して書く際は分解を具体的に書かなくても良いですが、今は例を扱っているため丁寧に書くと）",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca68",
      "text": " [$ \\begin{aligned}\\mathfrak{P}(X_{3})&=\\{\\emptyset\\}\\sqcup \\{\\{1\\},\\{2\\},\\{3\\}\\} \\sqcup \\{\\{1,2\\},\\{2,3\\},\\{1,3\\}\\} \\sqcup \\{\\{1,2,3\\}\\} \\\\ &=\\bigsqcup_{m=0}^{3}\\{A\\in\\mathfrak{P}(X_{3}) ; |A|=m\\}\\end{aligned}]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407836
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca69",
      "text": " となり（[$ |A\\sqcup B|=|A|+|B|]に注意して）",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca6a",
      "text": " [$ |\\mathfrak{P}(X_{3})|=\\sum_{m=0}^{3}|\\{A\\in\\mathfrak{P}(X_{3}) ; |A|=m\\}|=\\sum_{m=0}^{3}{}_{3}\\mathrm{C}_{m}]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca6b",
      "text": "　を得ます。最後の和は[二項定理]の具体例[$ \\sum_{m=0}^{3}{}_{3}\\mathrm{C}_{m}x^{m}=(1+x)^{3}]で[$ x=1]とおけば[$ 2^{3}]になることが分かります",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "63906604e600350000a1ca6c",
      "text": "　以上の例における[$ 3]を[$ n]に変えて全体を良い感じに書き直すと、一般の場合の証明になります",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407685,
      "updated": 1670407685
    },
    {
      "id": "639068275e90c0000076daee",
      "text": "　ありがとうございます[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670408230,
      "updated": 1670408242
    },
    {
      "id": "639068345e90c0000076daef",
      "text": "　　これは…………どうしたものかな",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670408243,
      "updated": 1670408277
    },
    {
      "id": "639068565e90c0000076daf0",
      "text": "　　思ってたよりも相当レベルの高い地帯に迷い込んでたのに気づいたときの気持ち",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670408277,
      "updated": 1670408395
    },
    {
      "id": "639068da5e90c0000007340d",
      "text": "   これ単体で読解しないとどうにもならん",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670408410,
      "updated": 1670408420
    },
    {
      "id": "639068fa5e90c0000007340e",
      "text": "   [「問：n個の要素からなる集合の部分集合は全部で2^n個あることを示せ hatoriさんヒント」の読解]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670408442,
      "updated": 1670408481
    },
    {
      "id": "63906602e600350000a1ca4e",
      "text": "　　見た目/言葉遣いが仰々しいのでぎょっとされたかもしれませんね...[hatori.icon]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670407683,
      "updated": 1670414360
    },
    {
      "id": "63908017e600350000eec84d",
      "text": "   [オフチョベットしたテフをマブガッドしてリットにする様子]みたいな",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670414360,
      "updated": 1670414360
    },
    {
      "id": "63908017e600350000eec84e",
      "text": "   とはいえ、日常的な言葉というか口語で説明されていたことを[数学語](?)に書き直しただけなので、噛み砕けばそんなに高尚なことはしていないはず",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670414360,
      "updated": 1670414390
    },
    {
      "id": "63908015e600350000eec84c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1670414358,
      "updated": 1670414358
    },
    {
      "id": "638f56eaaff09e0000573aa0",
      "text": "[問：n個の要素からなる集合の部分集合は全部で2^n個あることを示せ 別解(ネタバレ注意)]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338282,
      "updated": 1670338311
    },
    {
      "id": "638f56ebaff09e0000573aa1",
      "text": " ネタバレが生えてきた！[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670338283,
      "updated": 1670338325
    },
    {
      "id": "638f571b5e90c00000b37953",
      "text": "  解けるまで見ないぞ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670338332,
      "updated": 1670338339
    },
    {
      "id": "638f57115e90c00000b37952",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1670338322,
      "updated": 1670338322
    },
    {
      "id": "638f5c3ce5172d000098faf8",
      "text": "まあ和の計算はメインテーマではない気もしますが…[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1670339644,
      "updated": 1670339713
